{"tid":1833343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"場武漢肺炎漫延得咁快 其中原因係有支那人惡意傳播","createTime":"2020-01-21T23:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T01:24:50.000Z","uid":199727,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3e805c362f69a1ef958285f1aff1292aa608c2","tid":1833343,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T23:59:01.000Z","msg":"有人將惡意傳播當成向社會報復既手段<br />\n<br />\n支那大部分都係窮人，因此患上肺炎大部分都係窮人。喺支那，窮人已失去所有反抗既機會，一方面係因為社會流動性低，另一方面係因為言論自由已被收窄。<br />\n<br />\n對佢地黎講，惡意傳播就可以做到報復社會，同社會攬炒既結果。"},{"pid":"f23eb46015ecefa15ca71471e2a777a9a59c921c","tid":1833343,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T00:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2060439c71ceb60d5865b86042a77f50f676456","tid":1833343,"uid":87909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T00:21:23.000Z","msg":"似係班豬本身冇衛生意識"},{"pid":"0458510dde5e929643accf9d0dee29a69a2c44d9","tid":1833343,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"幾有道理，唔係就解釋唔到通街人知自己病都唔戴口罩"},{"pid":"f54935d19958ddf22a6a719a4ca5dcf3b6f89b7e","tid":1833343,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T00:24:33.000Z","msg":"唔好on9<br />\n低知識嘅人不知幾跟黨走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a52572315e7c08f5462de9a7409f0f17447e42","tid":1833343,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"傳黎傳去死既都係窮人多"},{"pid":"44d5eb3c45713a15752a3b06155fe7edcb993d68","tid":1833343,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T01:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877d1c8ec4dac7ec9c7986abc1b0d8c738b16e81","tid":1833343,"uid":30762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0458510dde5e929643accf9d0dee29a69a2c44d9","tid":1833343,"uid":331421,"like":